name: Tula Ng Ina Mo
description: "Tula Ng Ina Mo" is a poetry event that was held last February 03, 2017 (5years ago). I cannot draw an image that time so I need to copy from different works to create this piece. Ria Bautista of Paramita band was also a organizer of this event. A collaboration performances from Quezon Province, Manila and Cavite Spoken word and HipHop artist. Happy 5th birthday Tula Ng Ina MO!
